Dialogs.Dialog: Hey, I've found someone I like.
Eh... So, a character in a novel？ Or a character in a game？
Nope... wait, this is not a quiz.
You have no idea what I'm talking about？ Hah... Rinko is worried about you.
What do you mean？ I'm the one who's worried about you.
I'm sorry... I can't believe you took it that seriously.
(No, I can't do anything because I'm worried, ▲小早川＊▲...)
First, calm down. Close your eyes.
I'm really sorry. I didn't think...
"I've found someone I like" "Hey, it's April Fool's Day！" I though something like that.
Quite a bit. But I don't hate that part either. I'm sorry, forgive me.
Oh, I see, Golden Week. That's it？
Golden Week, or rather, the three days from the 3rd to the 5th.
They say that if couples kiss for a long time every day during that time, your relationship with them will grow rapidly.
Don't be silly, don't take it seriously.
(Then why did you tell me that？)
Golden Week kisses. Don't you remember？
I don't see how this is going to make any difference.
(I feel like I could be more intimate with you ▲小早川＊▲...)
I don't really care, so that's fine.
Golden Week kiss. I knew you forgot.
As I said, I don't mind.
(Today is the opening of the pool. It's joint with another grade, so ▲小早川＊▲...)
Ah, nothing... I like that ▲小早川＊▲！
I don't know what that means. Why don't you clarify？
Over all, you're the cutest ▲小早川＊▲.
...I'm not happy to be compared to others.
(Looks like I'll be looking forward to more pool lessons！)
(Today is the opening of the pool. It's joint with another grade, so ▲小早川＊▲...)
Not looking！ ...Well, I'm not staring at you. Perhaps.
Any closer and I'll kick you.
And if you stare at other girls, I will sue you for sexual harassment to the teacher.
Is it better to be kicked？
(Looks like I'll be looking forward to more pool lessons！)
(Today is the opening of the pool. It's joint with another grade, so ▲小早川＊▲...)
Hehe. It's refreshing to be in a school pool.
Don't stare too much. They're all around you.
(Looks like I'll be looking forward to more pool lessons！)
If you're not busy, come hang out with me.
Yeah, what are you doing？ Do you want me to time you？
No, that' s a hassle. Just reading. It's like being a book club member, right？
Because everyone is just playing pool. Then what do you care what they do？
How long can you stay underwater？
Hmm... who knows. Maybe a minute？
Then, try to dive for three minutes. If you succeed, I'll give you some potato chips from the library.
Hah, why 3 minutes！？ And the rewards are too low！
You know, Rinko... She seems like a child, right？
Huh？ Why are you asking me that？
Because if everyone wears the same swimsuit... you know.
Really？ I didn't know because I didn't see anyone other than you, ▲小早川＊▲.
I thought the pool was a pain in the ass, but it's pretty nice. It's mostly free time.
I've rested enough, maybe I'll go for a swim.
Oh, you want to have a race？
I won't do it. Come on, let's go.
My bad. I didn't realize it would be such a surprise.
I thought I was going to stop breathing... So you would have to give me artificial respiration.
Idiot！ Of course it's a lie. Idiot, dumbass！
I was... I'll tickle you to get even.
Whoa, hey！ Don't say that stuff out loud！
I wonder if houses with small children decorate bamboo branches and make wishes.
Me too... Well, there are a lot of places that do it, aren't there？
I see. The Kobayakawa Family also have a younger children, too.
Yes. So I'm having trouble for that.
Hey, what you said earlier about Tanabata. What's bothering you？
Because... doesn't it look good for Rinko to make a wish on a strip of paper？
You think？ I guess I'm surprised you like that kind of thing, ▲小早川＊▲.
I know it sounds like a lot of tricky stuff, but... Rinko has a proper line for Rinko to say.
Hmm. So, you're wondering if you should go out with me for my brother's sake？
Yes, it's a struggle between emotion and attitude.
I don't understand. What do you mean？
That's a... obsession that is hard to explain！
Hey, for Tanabata... I've decided to do it after all.
I see. I hope he'll be pleased.
Yeah, I'm sure it will be fine.
I guess you're an adult when you're dealing with your little brother ▲小早川＊▲.
I've always been an adult, right？ I have a boyfriend.
Then, so it's because of me？
Don't get carried away, but yeah, I guess you're right. I appreciate it, so thank you.
(It's over... It's a hassle to come to school just for this.)
You don't have to go that fast. I wanted to see you, ▲小早川＊▲.
I don't care, you can see me anytime.
Goodness, my boyfriend gets so lonely...
(It's over... It's a hassle to come to school just for this.)
Nothing, I don't have any reason to call you.
Then it's all fine. You can at least pass the time.
(It's over... It's a hassle to come to school just for this.)
Somehow, I wanted to come here. It's nice once in a while, isn't it？
It's fine, but... just once in a while？
I'm not going to get into the details.
(Hmm. It's a hassle coming just for the first day of school.)
It's a hassle coming just for the first day of school.
Because I was thinking the same thing.
(Hmm. It's a hassle coming just for the first day of school.)
Don't look so gloomy, it makes me gloomy too.
Oh, my bad. But I don't want to come, after all.
Naturally. You can't say it, so don't say it.
(Hmm. It's a hassle coming just for the first day of school.)
Hey, want to go to the arcade？
You've been practicing a lot, haven't you？
I appreciate your efforts, but since you're here, why don't you take a look at the results as well？ I'll take a look for you.
You know, I really don't want to leave, but I've been forced into a three- legged race.
Haha, I see. Well, don't give up and do your best.
But I still have to find a partner.
Ah, that's how it is. Okay, we'll leave together then.
Of course. Well, let's do some light practice.
Hmm, what？ Come on, let's go.
It's nothing！ ...I'm just trying to get to work.
Hah, I'm shocked... Maybe we are incompatible by any chance？
I think you got your breath back. It's more a matter of fitness.
For Rinko, right？ You were doing your best.
That's okay. Because this is now a memory.
If it's with you, it would not be too bad, ▲小早川＊▲.
Kidding. Thanks, I'm glad you helped me...
What do you do on Halloween？
Ah, so it's today. I don't have any plans.
I know, right？ It's quite a hassle to dress up and all that.
Maybe so, but... it would be fun if we could.
Why？ Do you have plans, ▲小早川＊▲？
I don't... but I wonder what I should do.
(I don't even have a TV to watch. What should I do...)
That's not what I meant. For now, please come in.
So, what's going on？ What happened today？
Nothing. I'm going to go get ready. Don't come this way.
Now, what was it... Give me candy or I'll give you a small kick！
Well, that's... So this is what you were thinking about when we were talking about Halloween.
Yeah. Rinko had a lot of fun. How about you？
I don't know if I was embarrassed or nervous.
I sent you on your way after I pushed you away. I'm sorry.
Okay, that's fine. I'll see you later.
(I did a great job on the management committee. I hope they succeed...)
...Yo. What's that class over there doing？
Historical data exhibit of the City of Towano.
That's okay, it's easy. You're a management committee member, right？ Are you busy？
I don't have that much work today.
By the way, what's with the outfit？
When I skipped all the prep work, the sensei made me tout the exhibition. Touting a boring exhibit is really the worst...
(I feel bad for her... but she got what she deserved.)
(I'm glad the Cultural Festival went off without a hitch. Now all that's left is the party.)
But the festival itself was a success, right？ Thanks to you.
I don't know if it was thanks to me or not, but I'm glad for it.
Hmm. You know what, come hang out with me for a minute.
There's a place I'd like you to go with me.
Nobody's here. This rooftop is a nice place, but not very popular.
Yup. That's why... I called you up here back then.
It's my favorite place, and no one can get in my way... that's why I like it here.
Every time I come here, I'm reminded of it. I can't come here casually anymore, and it's a nice nuisance.
I don't really care about that. It's more like... I'm remembering it again right now.
Can you do the same thing you did back then？
Hi. Summer classes start today. Hah...
Why are you talking like it is someone else's problem？
Hey, how can we get rid of summer school？ What if you break all the windows at the school now？
That would not be the end of summer school, but my whole student life.
Good morning. Hope the summer classes go by fast！
Hi. I'm sick of summer classes.
Sick, you say. You didn't want to do it from the beginning.
It's hot. Why bother with summer classes when it's hot？
That's because it's the summer season.
Good morning. I'm tired of summer school. Should I skip it？
I understand how you feel, but you have to be patient.
Hi. Did you know？ I heard that the winter semester starts today.
Huh？ Yeah. That's why we are here, right？
What, I knew it was real...
Do Rinko looks like she wants to take winter classes？
If that was the case, you should have done something about it before today. It's inexcusable...
Good morning. Winter term starts today. Circle？ Or, Cross？
Hi. Hey, didn't you already complete the course when you woke up in the morning with the cold？
I think Rinko might have caught a cold.
What？ Are you sure you're okay to come？
...Sorry, a lie. I wish my mom could be fooled too.
Don't say things you can't do.
(What do you want me to do...？)
Hi. Spring semester starts today, huh. I wonder how many times I'll doze off...
At any rate, I guess I'm supposed to doze off.
Alright, spring semester. I'll do my best starting today！
Good morning. The spring semester starts today. Will it be over by tomorrow？
As I said, it's not that short.
I know. I checked it many times.
Hi. I'll try not to sleep today.
Oh, that's a good mindset, isn't it？
That's what I thought last time.
Good morning. The course is almost over.
Well... I guess？ Are you going to miss them？
Oh, by the way, did you hear about the contest, ▲小早川＊▲？
They are going to held a swimsuit contest.
There's some kind of buzz going around.
Surprisingly, you might get selected to enter, ▲小早川＊▲？
I don't want to look like a freak show.
You didn't want to do it？
It's complicated, but... it's good. That means you will be more proud of your girlfriend.
